Penis envy
[[Penis envy]] is a [[FACT|claim]] often thrown around in [[libel|internet]] [[defamation|arguments]] involving [[feminazi]]s, [[asspies]], and otherwise [[Canada|Canadian]] people, as an [[ad hominem]] attack meant to show what a [[douchebag]] they are.  The key is to diagnose them in the most [[troll|condescending, yet scholarly way possible]].
[[Image:Lacanphallus.JPG|thumb|Jacques Lacan has a phallus and it's the center of the [[shit nobody cares about|symbolic order]].]]
[[Image:Bbeavercanhasphallus.JPG|thumb|As a female, [[BitingBeaver]] lacks a phallus, and can only have one through giving birth to a future rapist.]]
==Penis envy as an argument tactic==
Remember, anyone who has penis envy is not equipped to argue anything, as they wish they had a penis and/or balls:
